        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p>Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information in the CRFV Event System.</p>
            <div class="last-update">
                <i class="fas fa-history"></i> Last Updated: July 10, 2025
            </div>
